document.full_text: a fresh explosion rocked japan's quake-stricken nuclear power complex on tuesday, around its overheating no.2 reactor, but there was no immediate word of any damage to the reactor itself, the country's nuclear safety agency said.
document.title: new hydrogen explosion rocks stricken japan reactor
